15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 37A O.S. 2021, Section 2-129, is
16 amended to read as follows:
17 Section 2-129. A. A charitable auction or charitable alcoholic
18 beverage event license may be issued to a charitable organization
19 exempt from taxation under Section 501(c)(3), (4) 501(c)(4), (5)
20 501(c)(5), (6) 501(c)(6), (7) 501(c)(7), (8) 501(c)(8), (9)
21 501(c)(9), (10) 501(c)(10) or (19) 501(c)(19) of the United States
22 Internal Revenue Code of 1986, as amended. The charitable alcoholic
23 beverage event license shall authorize the holder thereof to conduct
24 a wine, spirit and/or beer event which may consist of one or more of
