16 pursuant to this subsection. The maximum amount of wine, spirits
17 and/or beer auctioned pursuant to the charitable auction license
18 shall not exceed fifty (50) gallons. All wines, beer and spirits
19 auctioned pursuant to the charitable auction license shall be
20 registered and all fees and taxes shall be paid in accordance with
21 the Oklahoma Alcoholic Beverage Control Act.
22 F. No charitable alcoholic beverage event license shall be
23 required for an organization, association or nonprofit corporation
24 which is an economic development chamber or similar entity, provided
